   - Tap "Text" â†’ Type Line 1 â†’ Position at center
   - Set timing: 0:00 - 0:02
   - Add animation: "Fade In"
   - Repeat for Lines 2-5, each 2 seconds apart
7. Add sound: Tap "Audio" â†’ "Sounds" â†’ Search trending or use dramatic music
