>
> SUPPORT
> â—¾ Price level where buying interest appeared
> â—¾ "Floor" that held price up
> â—¾ More touches = stronger level
>
> RESISTANCE
> â—¾ Price level where selling interest appeared
> â—¾ "Ceiling" that pushed price down
> â—¾ More touches = stronger level
>
