## POST 142 â€” ðŸŽ“ CORRELATION TRADING (Lesson 38)

**Source:** https://education.signalpilot.io/curriculum/intermediate/38-correlation-trading.html

### ð• Twitter

**Copy:**
> BTC moves. ETH follows. Most of the time.
>
> Correlation: When assets move together.
>
> Positive correlation = Move same direction
> Negative correlation = Move opposite
>
> Don't trade correlated assets as separate bets. You're doubling risk, not diversifying.

**Image:** Correlation chart showing BTC/ETH moving together

**Hashtags:** #Correlation #CorrelationTrading #TradingEducation #SignalPilot #RiskManagement

---

### ðŸ“¸ Instagram

**Caption:**
> Correlation Trading 101 ðŸ”—
>
> WHAT IS CORRELATION?
> The degree to which assets move together
>
> POSITIVE CORRELATION (+1)
> â—¾ Assets move in same direction
> â—¾ BTC & ETH, EUR/USD & GBP/USD
> â—¾ Trading both = doubling exposure
>
> NEGATIVE CORRELATION (-1)
> â—¾ Assets move opposite
> â—¾ USD/JPY & Gold (often)
> â—¾ Can be used for hedging
>
> NO CORRELATION (0)
> â—¾ Assets move independently
> â—¾ True diversification
>
> THE DANGER:
> Thinking you're diversified when you're just doubling risk.
>
> Full lesson in bio ðŸ”—

**Image:** 1080x1080 â€” Correlation matrix showing different asset relationships

**Hashtags:** #Correlation #CorrelationTrading #PortfolioRisk #Diversification #SignalPilot #CryptoTrading #ForexTrading #TradingEducation #AssetCorrelation #RiskManagement #LearnTrading #TradingStrategy #DoubleExposure #CorrelationMatrix #SmartTrading

---

### ðŸŽ¬ TikTok

**Hook:** "You're not diversified. You're doubling risk."

**On-Screen Text:**
| Time | Text |
|------|------|
| 0-2s | THINK YOU'RE DIVERSIFIED? |
| 2-4s | BTC long âœ… |
| 4-5s | ETH long âœ… |
| 5-7s | They're 95% CORRELATED |
| 7-9s | That's not diversification |
| 9-11s | That's DOUBLE exposure |
| 11-13s | Learn correlation. Manage risk. |

**Background:** Chart showing BTC and ETH moving identically

**Sound:** Warning/realization sound

**Duration:** 13 seconds

**Step-by-Step Creation:**
1. Find chart showing BTC/ETH correlation
2. Overlay them to show similarity
3. Open CapCut â†’ Import
4. Add text at timestamps
5. Show the correlation visually
6. Warning sound, 25% volume
7. Export 1080x1920
8. Caption: "Correlation is risk. #trading #correlation"

