> RETRACEMENTS vs EXTENSIONS:
> â—¾ Retracements = Where pullbacks may end
> â—¾ Extensions = Where moves may go
>
> KEY EXTENSION LEVELS:
>
> ðŸ“ 1.272 (127.2%)
> First extension target
> Conservative profit area
>
> ðŸ“ 1.618 (161.8%)
> Golden ratio extension
> Most watched level
>
> ðŸ“ 2.0 (200%)
> Double the initial move
> Strong target zone
>
> ðŸ“ 2.618 (261.8%)
> Extended target
> Strong trends only
>
> HOW TO USE:
> Draw from swing low to high (uptrend)
> Extensions project above the high
>
> Full lesson in bio ðŸ”—

