## POST 194 â€” ðŸ’¬ QUOTE CARD

**Source:** Signal Pilot Philosophy

### ð• Twitter

**Copy:**
> "Successful trading is about managing risk, not avoiding it."
>
> Risk is unavoidable.
> Unmanaged risk is catastrophic.
> Managed risk is opportunity.
