>
> It means over many trades, the math works out.
>
> Trust the process, not the individual result."

**Image:** Dark quote card with text, orange accent, Signal Pilot branding

**Hashtags:** #TradingEdge #Process #SignalPilot #TradingMindset

---

### ðŸ“¸ Instagram

**Caption:**
> ðŸŽ² EDGE VS OUTCOME
>
> "An edge doesn't mean every trade wins.
>
> It means over many trades, the math works out.
>
> Trust the process, not the individual result."
>
> Understanding edge:
>
> âœ¦ CASINO ANALOGY
> â†’ Casino has edge on every game
> â†’ They still lose individual hands
> â†’ Over thousands of hands, they win
>
> âœ¦ YOUR EDGE WORKS THE SAME
> â†’ Positive expectancy over time
> â†’ Individual trades are random
> â†’ Large sample = results
>
> What this means:
>
> âœ… Losing trades don't mean broken strategy
> âœ… Winning trades don't mean perfect strategy
> âœ… Judge after 50-100 trades minimum
>
> One trade is noise.
>
> Many trades reveal truth.
>
> Save this ðŸ“Œ

