> ðŸ“Š INDECISION PATTERNS:
>
> âœ¦ DOJI
> â†’ Open and close nearly equal
> â†’ Market undecided
> â†’ Potential reversal or continuation
>
> ðŸ”„ REVERSAL PATTERNS:
>
> âœ¦ HAMMER / HANGING MAN
> â†’ Long lower wick, small body
> â†’ Rejection of lower prices
> â†’ Bullish at support, bearish at resistance
>
> âœ¦ ENGULFING
> â†’ Current candle engulfs previous
> â†’ Bullish engulfing = buyers took control
> â†’ Bearish engulfing = sellers took control
>
> âœ¦ MORNING/EVENING STAR
> â†’ Three-candle pattern
> â†’ Reversal at key levels
>
> Important:
>
> âœ¦ Context matters (where on chart?)
> âœ¦ Volume confirms
> âœ¦ Higher TF = more reliable
> âœ¦ Pattern â‰  guarantee
