---

### ð• Twitter

**Copy:**
> Is smart money accumulating or distributing?
>
> Plutus Flow shows flow directionâ€”where value is building vs where it's exiting.
>
> Accumulation often precedes markup. Distribution often precedes markdown.
>
> Demo: [link]

**Image:** Plutus Flow showing accumulation and distribution phases on chart

**Hashtags:** #PlutusFlow #Accumulation #Distribution #SignalPilot #TradingView

---

### ðŸ“¸ Instagram

**Caption:**
> âš–ï¸ PLUTUS FLOW: ACCUMULATION VS DISTRIBUTION
>
> Where is value flowing?
>
> ðŸ“¦ ACCUMULATION PHASE
> â†’ Flow building (positive)
> â†’ Smart money buying
> â†’ Often occurs in ranges
> â†’ Precedes markup (potentially)
>
> ðŸ“¤ DISTRIBUTION PHASE
> â†’ Flow declining (negative)
> â†’ Smart money selling
> â†’ Often occurs at tops
> â†’ Precedes markdown (potentially)
>
> What Plutus Flow shows:
>
> âœ¦ FLOW DIRECTION
> â†’ Green = accumulation
> â†’ Red = distribution
>
> âœ¦ FLOW STRENGTH
> â†’ Intensity of the flow
> â†’ Strong vs weak conviction
>
> âœ¦ DIVERGENCES
> â†’ Price up, flow down = warning
> â†’ Price down, flow up = potential reversal
>
> Context for the Wyckoff cycle.
>
> See it in action ðŸ”— Link in bio
>
> âš ï¸ Educational demo. Not financial advice.

