---

### ðŸ“¸ Instagram

**Caption:**
> ðŸŽ¯ ENTRY TECHNIQUES
>
> How you enter affects your trade.
>
> ðŸ“Š ORDER TYPES:
>
> âš¡ MARKET ORDER
> â†’ Immediate execution
> â†’ Current price
> â†’ Guaranteed fill
> â†’ May get slippage
>
> ðŸŽ¯ LIMIT ORDER
> â†’ Specify your price
> â†’ Better entry if filled
> â†’ Might miss the trade
> â†’ No slippage
>
> ðŸš€ STOP ORDER
> â†’ Triggered when price hits level
> â†’ Confirmation of breakout
> â†’ Often worse price
> â†’ Ensures momentum behind entry
>
> ðŸ“ CHOOSING YOUR ENTRY:
>
> âœ¦ AGGRESSIVE (Limit/Market)
> â†’ Better price
> â†’ Less confirmation
> â†’ Higher risk of wrong direction
>
> âœ¦ CONSERVATIVE (Stop/Confirmation)
> â†’ Worse price
> â†’ More confirmation
> â†’ Higher probability of right direction
>
> No right answer. Matches your strategy.
>
