**Hashtags:** #MarketTypes #TradingBasics #SignalPilot #TradingEducation

---

### ðŸ“¸ Instagram

**Caption:**
> ðŸ“Š MARKET TYPES
>
> Different markets need different approaches.
>
> ðŸ“ˆ TRENDING MARKET
>
> â†’ Clear direction (up or down)
> â†’ Higher highs/lows or lower highs/lows
> â†’ Strategy: Follow the trend
> â†’ Tools: MAs, structure, momentum
>
> â†”ï¸ RANGING MARKET
>
> â†’ No clear direction
> â†’ Price bouncing between S/R
> â†’ Strategy: Buy support, sell resistance
> â†’ Tools: S/R levels, oscillators
>
> ðŸ’¥ VOLATILE/CHOPPY MARKET
>
> â†’ Erratic, no structure
> â†’ False breakouts everywhere
> â†’ Strategy: Reduce size or stay flat
> â†’ Wait for clarity
>
> ðŸŽ¯ KEY PRINCIPLE:
>
> â†’ Identify market type FIRST
> â†’ Then choose appropriate strategy
> â†’ Trend strategy in range = failure
> â†’ Range strategy in trend = failure
>
> Context before action.
>
> Free lesson ðŸŽ“ Link in bio
>
> âš ï¸ Educational only. Not financial advice.

