### ðŸ“¸ Instagram

**Caption:**
> ðŸ“ˆ VOLATILITY CYCLES
>
> Volatility breathes in and out.
>
> THE CYCLE:
>
> ðŸ”¹ COMPRESSION (Low Vol)
> â†’ Tight ranges
> â†’ Small candles
> â†’ Decreasing ATR
> â†’ Energy building
>
> ðŸ”¸ EXPANSION (High Vol)
> â†’ Wide ranges
> â†’ Large candles
> â†’ Increasing ATR
> â†’ Energy releasing
>
> THE PATTERN:
> â†’ Low vol doesn't last forever
> â†’ High vol doesn't last forever
> â†’ They rotate continuously
>
> TRADING IMPLICATIONS:
>
> ðŸ“‰ DURING COMPRESSION:
> â†’ Prepare for expansion
> â†’ Watch for breakout setups
> â†’ Position for the move
>
> ðŸ“ˆ DURING EXPANSION:
> â†’ Ride the momentum
> â†’ Watch for exhaustion
> â†’ Expect eventual compression
>
